GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/health


### Create Pricing Enquiry
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/enquiry
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channel": "whatsapp",
  "customer_name": "Priya S",
  "message": "Hi, what is your pricing?"
}


### Create Booking Enquiry
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/enquiry
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channel": "call",
  "customer_name": "Rohan M",
  "message": "I want to book a demo meeting."
}


### Create Unknown Enquiry For Auto Escalation
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/enquiry
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channel": "email",
  "customer_name": "Alex K",
  "message": "Blue mango laptop river."
}


### Get Enquiry History
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/enquiry/1/history


### Schedule Follow-Up
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/enquiry/1/follow-up
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "delay_minutes": 30,
  "message_template": "Hi, just checking if you had a chance to review our pricing."
}


### Escalate Enquiry
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/enquiry/1/escalate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Customer requested human support."
}